OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1780495874
OL,3,CArmed police race to street near
OL,4,Cschool after reports of man armed with
OL,5,Cknife
OL,7,FWarning: Distressing Footage
OL,9,FArmed police raced to a street near a
OL,10,Fschool in Salford on Tuesday morning
OL,11,F(June 2) following reports of a man
OL,12,Farmed with a knife.
OL,14,FOfficers attended the incident on
OL,15,FLiverpool Road and New Moss Road in
OL,16,Fthe Irlam and Cadishead areas at
OL,17,Faround 9am.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
