FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1780495874
OL,3,CArmed police race to street near
OL,4,Cschool after reports of man armed with
OL,5,Cknife
OL,7,FDramatic body-worn footage from
OL,8,FGreater Manchester Police (GMP)
OL,9,Fofficers showed the moment the suspect
OL,10,Fwas Tasered and fell to the ground
OL,11,Fwhile holding the blade. Shouts of
OL,12,F'put it down' could be heard moments
OL,13,Fbefore the man was then detained.
OL,15,FA man in his 60s was found to be in
OL,16,Fpossession of the blade. He was then
OL,17,Farrested on suspicion of possession of
OL,18,Fan offensive weapon and remains in
OL,19,Fcustody for questioning.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
