FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1780495874
OL,3,CArmed police race to street near
OL,4,Cschool after reports of man armed with
OL,5,Cknife
OL,7,FPolice said the taser was used to
OL,8,Fensure the suspect was safely detained
OL,9,Fand was 'in line with specialist
OL,10,Ftraining'.
OL,12,FDetective Chief Superintendent Neil
OL,13,FJones, of GMP, said: "Public safety
OL,14,Fremains our absolute priority.
OL,16,F"Today's incident demonstrates both
OL,17,Fthe effectiveness of rapid public
OL,18,Freporting and the professionalism of
OL,19,Four officers in responding to a
OL,20,Fpotentially dangerous situation.
OL,26,@uD@VOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
