OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1780495874
OL,3,CArmed police race to street near
OL,4,Cschool after reports of man armed with
OL,5,Cknife
OL,7,F"The deployment of the Taser 10 ` the
OL,8,Ffirst incident where we have used the
OL,9,Fnew technology - provided officers
OL,10,Fwith a critical less-lethal option to
OL,11,Fresolve the incident safely and
OL,12,Fproportionately.
OL,14,F"GMP continues to invest in training
OL,15,Fand the latest technology to ensure
OL,16,Fofficers are equipped to respond to
OL,17,Femerging threats while maintaining the
OL,18,Fhighest standards of accountability
OL,19,Fand public trust.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
