OL,3,CArmed police race to street near
OL,4,Cschool after reports of man armed with
OL,5,Cknife
OL,7,F"Uniformed officers will remain in the
OL,8,Farea to provide a visible and
OL,9,Freassuring presence for the local
OL,10,Fcommunity following this incident. If
OL,11,Fyou have any concerns, please speak to
OL,12,Fthem."
